<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>After-Party</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Banner Section -->
  <section class="after-party-hero">
    <h1>After-Party</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Celebrate the night away with laughter, music, and memories!</p>
  </section>

    <!-- Description Section -->
    <section class="description-section-afterparty">
      <p>
        The wedding after-party is an exciting and informal celebration that takes place after the main reception. It’s the perfect way to keep the energy alive, allowing guests to unwind, enjoy music, savor snacks, and share memorable moments in a relaxed atmosphere.
        <br />
        Whether it’s a cozy lounge or an outdoor setting, the after-party lets everyone continue the festivities long into the night, adding a personalized touch to your special day.
      </p>
    </section>

 <!-- Content Section -->
  <section class="after-party-content">

    <div class="detail-box-afterparty">
      <div class="box-content-afterparty">
        <img src="https://blacktie.com/cdn/shop/products/madison-heather-grey-1024x_800x.jpg?v=1654778386" alt="Cozy lounge setting" class="box-image-afterparty" />
        <div class="text-content-afterparty">
          <h3>Keep it Casual and Fun</h3>
          <p>
            Choose a relaxed dress code to create a laid-back and welcoming vibe. Guests will feel comfortable while still enjoying the special occasion.
          </p>
          <div class="advice-box-afterparty">
            <span class="advice-title">⭐ Advice from FIORE:</span>
            <p>Set up cozy lounge areas with soft lighting to create a warm and inviting atmosphere.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="button-group-afterparty">
            <a href="/GiftShops" target="_blank" class="luxury-button-afterparty">Explore Shops</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="detail-box-afterparty">
      <div class="box-content-afterparty">
        <img src="https://www.brides.com/thmb/yRd7LwudPTul2_2pfM8FUzGwhfs=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/15-colorful-dress-san-francisco-wedding-cocktails-olivia-marshall-0424-fe63d88e0b1143f5a42a84d0116d2ca3.jpg" alt="Elegant cocktails" class="box-image-afterparty" />
        <div class="text-content-afterparty">
          <h3>Offer Signature Drinks</h3>
          <p>
            Personalized drinks are a great way to add a special touch. Include options that reflect the couple's taste or the theme of the evening.
          </p>
          <div class="advice-box-afterparty">
            <span class="advice-title">⭐ Advice from FIORE:</span>
            <p>Use elegant glassware and garnishes like edible flowers or fruit slices for a stylish presentation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="detail-box-afterparty">
      <div class="box-content-afterparty">
        <img src="https://mydjs.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/IMG_1548.jpg" alt="DJ or music setup" class="box-image-afterparty" />
        <div class="text-content-afterparty">
          <h3>Music That Sets the Mood</h3>
          <p>
            A chill music playlist or live DJ can keep the energy alive. Focus on tracks that encourage dancing or easy conversation.
          </p>
          <div class="advice-box-afterparty">
            <span class="advice-title">⭐ Advice from FIORE:</span>
            <p>Create a mix of upbeat and mellow tracks to cater to all guests' preferences.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="button-group-afterparty">
            <a href="/DJ" target="_blank" class="luxury-button-afterparty">Explore DJs/Bands</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
      
    <div class="detail-box-afterparty">
      <div class="box-content-afterparty">
        <img src="https://i0.wp.com/foodtobring.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Cheap-Finger-Foods-for-Wedding-Reception.png?resize=680%2C680&ssl=1" alt="Delicious light snacks" class="box-image-afterparty" />
        <div class="text-content-afterparty">
          <h3>Light Snacks for the Night</h3>
          <p>
            Keep the menu simple with easy-to-eat finger foods. Think sliders, mini desserts, and other bite-sized treats.
          </p>
          <div class="advice-box-afterparty">
            <span class="advice-title">⭐ Advice from FIORE:</span>
            <p>Provide vegetarian and allergy-friendly options to ensure all guests are accommodated.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>
</body>
</html>

